<h2 id="加入-hugo-theme使用-git-submodule-方式"><strong>加入 Hugo theme</strong>（使用 git submodule 方式）</h2>
<p>Hugo 主題網站：<a href="https://themes.gohugo.io/">https://themes.gohugo.io/</a></p>
<div class="highlight"><div style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
<table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;"><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
<pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">1
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">2
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">3
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">4
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">5
</span></code></pre></td>
<td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
<pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span>git init
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>git submodule add --depth<span style="color:#f92672">=</span><span style="color:#ae81ff">1</span> https://github.com/adityatelange/hugo-PaperMod.git themes/PaperMod
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># 更新 theme</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>git submodule update --init --recursive
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p><strong>參考：三種 theme 安裝方式</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>
<p>使用 Git <strong><a href="https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2/Git-Tools-Submodules">submodules</a></strong> 建置 —&gt; 推薦</p>
<ul>
<li>能追蹤 theme 的升級，也算是能自己改動</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>手動 copy theme 檔案</p>
<ul>
<li>未來得自己手動升級</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p>當作 Hugo Module (當成 Go Module) 安裝</p>
<ul>
<li>升級 theme 較容易，但無法更動內部程式</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="修改-hugotoml指定-theme">修改 Hugo.toml，指定 theme</h3>
<div class="highlight"><div style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
<table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;"><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
<pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">1
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">2
</span></code></pre></td>
<td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
<pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-plain" data-lang="plain"><span style="display:flex;"><span># 增加這行，指定 theme
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>theme = &#39;PaperMod&#39;
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><hr>
<h2 id="執行網站">執行網站</h2>
<div class="highlight"><div style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
<table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;"><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
<pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">1
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">2
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">3
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">4
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">5
</span></code></pre></td>
<td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
<pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># 編譯時，連同草稿文件一起顯示 (文章檔案最上方參數 draft=true)</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>hugo server -D
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># 編譯時，不含草稿 (文章檔案最上方參數 draft=false)</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>hugo server
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><ul>
<li>
<p>執行指令後，會啟動 <a href="http://localhost:1313/">http://localhost:1313/</a>，可用 Browser 看網站</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>此時若修改 ./posts 目錄的文章，網頁會立即改變 (即時預覽)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="編譯網站">編譯網站</h2>
<div class="highlight"><div style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">
<table style="border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;"><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;">
<pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">1
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">2
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">3
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">4
</span><span style="white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f">5
</span></code></pre></td>
<td style="vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%">
<pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># 編譯網站，並輸出至 .\public 目錄</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>hugo
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span><span style="color:#75715e"># 編譯網站，並指定 baseurl</span>
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>hugo server -b https://jason1167.github.io
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h3 id="踩雷區">踩雷區</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>問題</strong>：編譯輸出後 (public 目錄)，html 檔內的網址路徑都是 http://localhost，造成上線後異常 (找不到檔案)。</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>解決</strong>：只要編譯時，加入指定 baseurl 即可 <code>hugo server -b ``&lt;https://jason1167.github.io&gt;</code></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content:encoded>
